            "userId": null,
            "sessionId": null,
            "public": false,
            "input": "Give me json structure",
            "output": "Here are a few examples of JSON structures:\n\n**Simple Example**\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"age\": 30,\n  \"city\": \"New York\"\n}\n```\n**Object with Array**\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"age\": 30,\n  \"cities\": [\n    \"New York\",\n    \"Los Angeles\",\n    \"Chicago\"\n  ]\n}\n```\n**Object with Nested Object**\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"age\": 30,\n  \"address\": {\n    \"street\": \"123 Main St\",\n    \"apartment\": 4,\n    \"city\": \"New York\",\n    \"state\": \"NY\"\n  }\n}\n```\n**Object with Multiple Arrays**\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"age\": 30,\n  \"hobbies\": [\n    \"reading\",\n    \"hiking\",\n    \"coding\"\n  ],\n  \"friends\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"Jane Doe\",\n      \"age\": 25\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"Bob Smith\",\n      \"age\": 35\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n**Object with Complex Structure**\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"type\": \"product\",\n  \"attributes\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"price\",\n      \"value\": 19.99\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"description\",\n      \"value\": \"This is a great product\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"relationships\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"category\",\n      \"id\": 5\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"tags\",\n      \"ids\": [1, 2, 3]\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\nLet me know if you'd like to see any specific examples!",
